  {
   "start": 0.0,
   "end": 8.48,
   "text": "...of force, 57 BC, destroyed by earthquakes in 522 and then in 551 AD, and it was big, okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 9.24,
   "end": 17.86,
   "text": "This is what it looks like, and the Zeusian, it was right in the middle of there, of the thing, the Olympia."
  },
  {
   "start": 18.54,
   "end": 19.76,
   "text": "That's what it looked like, okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 20.16,
   "end": 25.3,
   "text": "Now the statue of Zeus, which was carded off by the Justinian, I don't know whoever,"
  },
  {
   "start": 25.3,
   "end": 31.7,
   "text": "The Roman Emperor, when they closed down the Impa Games in 393 AD, was carded to Constantinople and then destroyed in a fire,"
  },
  {
   "start": 31.82,
   "end": 34.1,
   "text": "But that's how big that Zeus is, okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 34.58,
   "end": 36.32,
   "text": "Now look at this temple, this tower."
  },
  {
   "start": 37.14,
   "end": 41.08,
   "text": "Okay, that pillar is that pillar, right."
  },
  {
   "start": 41.58,
   "end": 46.6,
   "text": "So Zeus, Zeus's head was way above the top of that pillar."
  },
  {
   "start": 47.66,
   "end": 54.38,
   "text": "So Zeus's head sitting on the chair was way above the top of that, which is like really high."
  },
  {
   "start": 54.38,
   "end": 60.98,
   "text": "I think he was like 10 meters high, and those pedestals, those columns I was looking at,"
  },
  {
   "start": 61.02,
   "end": 64.88,
   "text": "That was just one of the columns, a huge column I was just looking at right there."
  },
  {
   "start": 66.16,
   "end": 71.74,
   "text": "You know, and if it's on its side, maybe seven feet tall, was this guy."
  },
  {
   "start": 71.74,
   "end": 78.3,
   "text": "So, very big statue of Zeus that they have here at the Temple of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 78.7,
   "end": 85.38,
   "text": "Here's the circular temple, the Temple of Hera."
  },
  {
   "start": 87.14,
   "end": 89.4,
   "text": "So let's go over here and see what this one says."
  },
  {
   "start": 92.42,
   "end": 93.46,
   "text": "And here's more parts."
  },
  {
   "start": 93.68,
   "end": 95.94,
   "text": "One that collapsed in the earthquake."
  },
  {
   "start": 95.94,
   "end": 104.36,
   "text": "Okay, yeah, that one was put back up for the Olympic Games of 2004."
  },
  {
   "start": 104.86,
   "end": 114.21,
   "text": "Give us an idea of how big the Temple of Zeus was."
  },
  {
   "start": 114.97,
   "end": 118.95,
   "text": "And these columns still exist, the bases of them."
  },
  {
   "start": 119.95,
   "end": 123.25,
   "text": "I think it was six columns along the side and like 12 along the edges."
  },
  {
   "start": 123.25,
   "end": 128.19,
   "text": "And there's the, uh, the hallway in there."
  },
  {
   "start": 128.51,
   "end": 132.51,
   "text": "Too bad you can't, um, see it, walk her down in there."
  },
  {
   "start": 132.73,
   "end": 135.81,
   "text": "But here's, here's one of the columns that fell."
  },
  {
   "start": 135.91,
   "end": 137.49,
   "text": "And there's what it looks like next to me."
  },
  {
   "start": 139.23,
   "end": 141.31,
   "text": "It did fit the whole thing in with me."
  },
  {
   "start": 141.63,
   "end": 143.8,
   "text": "It's very big."
  },
  {
   "start": 148.3,
   "end": 148.94,
   "text": "Another one."
  },
  {
   "start": 150.08,
   "end": 151.06,
   "text": "Oh, they just got it."
  },
  {
   "start": 152.14,
   "end": 153.94,
   "text": "Oh, they just fell all over."
  },
  {
   "start": 153.94,
   "end": 168.36,
   "text": "Okay, let's see where they worshipped Pelops, the hero complex."
  },
  {
   "start": 168.52,
   "end": 171.4,
   "text": "It must be where they hung out in this area here."
  },
  {
   "start": 173.6,
   "end": 176.36,
   "text": "But, well, this is pretty much all we have left of it, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 177.26,
   "end": 178.34,
   "text": "Not very interesting."
  },
  {
   "start": 178.52,
   "end": 179.66,
   "text": "Here's the Temple of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 181.42,
   "end": 183.04,
   "text": "Some American high school kids."
  },
  {
   "start": 185.94,
   "end": 189.36,
   "text": "There's the aqueduct in the circular temple."
  },
  {
   "start": 190.8,
   "end": 194.54,
   "text": "But, um, but, uh, Alexander the Great."
  },
  {
   "start": 194.86,
   "end": 197.61,
   "text": "Let me see."
  },
  {
   "start": 197.61,
   "end": 198.17,
   "text": "There's more."
  },
  {
   "start": 198.17,
   "end": 199.43,
   "text": "I wonder what that building is."
  },
  {
   "start": 199.51,
   "end": 200.27,
   "text": "Maybe we'll check it out."
  },
  {
   "start": 201.29,
   "end": 202.15,
   "text": "Let's go this way."
  },
  {
   "start": 204.28,
   "end": 205.2,
   "text": "These Teacodians."
  },
  {
   "start": 205.54,
   "end": 207.66,
   "text": "Well, the priests stayed."
  },
  {
   "start": 208.9,
   "end": 210.3,
   "text": "This area right there."
  },
  {
   "start": 211.3,
   "end": 212.46,
   "text": "That's what it looked like."
  },
  {
   "start": 214.08,
   "end": 217.52,
   "text": "But it's not very interesting in real life, as you can see."
  },
  {
   "start": 220.59,
   "end": 226.93,
   "text": "But it's situated next to the circular building, Temple of Hera, and the Temple of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 227.93,
   "end": 229.39,
   "text": "Up on a little false hill."
  },
  {
   "start": 229.39,
   "end": 234.89,
   "text": "There's another false hill where that other Temple of Pelos, or whatever it was, you can see."
  },
  {
   "start": 234.89,
   "end": 245.45,
   "text": "It's the workshop of Phaedos, where the guy made the temple, the, uh, Statue of Zeus, one of the wonders of the ancient world."
  },
  {
   "start": 245.45,
   "end": 246.45,
   "text": "That's what it looked like."
  },
  {
   "start": 246.45,
   "end": 247.45,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 247.45,
   "end": 248.45,
   "text": "That's what it looked like."
  },
  {
   "start": 248.45,
   "end": 257.77,
   "text": "And look, it still stands."
  },
  {
   "start": 257.77,
   "end": 258.77,
   "text": "It's pretty cool, huh?"
  },
  {
   "start": 258.77,
   "end": 260.77,
   "text": "It never, it never fell for a whole lot of years."
  },
  {
   "start": 260.77,
   "end": 261.77,
   "text": "It still stands."
  },
  {
   "start": 261.77,
   "end": 262.77,
   "text": "Big blocks in the bottom."
  },
  {
   "start": 262.77,
   "end": 275.69,
   "text": "And this is what Roman bricks look like."
  },
  {
   "start": 275.69,
   "end": 281.69,
   "text": "They're really flat, pancake-y, and long, instead of the short, fat ones we have these days."
  },
  {
   "start": 281.69,
   "end": 286.69,
   "text": "I noticed that when I was in Rome, back in 97."
  },
  {
   "start": 286.69,
   "end": 288.69,
   "text": "So let's go see what the inside look is like."
  },
  {
   "start": 288.69,
   "end": 290.69,
   "text": "Look at this stonework."
  },
  {
   "start": 290.69,
   "end": 295.79,
   "text": "Pretty artistic."
  },
  {
   "start": 295.79,
   "end": 309.05,
   "text": "There is the place where the artist, Phaedos, made his statue of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 309.05,
   "end": 318.05,
   "text": "And in here, the Greek baths, Phaedos Thermae, heated with water from underneath."
  },
  {
   "start": 318.05,
   "end": 322.05,
   "text": "And they still have very impressive mosaic."
  },
  {
   "start": 322.05,
   "end": 329.46,
   "text": "Right on the edge of the river."
  },
  {
   "start": 329.46,
   "end": 333.46,
   "text": "See, they heated up the water and made the baths."
  },
  {
   "start": 333.46,
   "end": 336.46,
   "text": "Here's the building."
  },
  {
   "start": 336.46,
   "end": 340.46,
   "text": "Um, here's the mosaic, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 340.46,
   "end": 347.46,
   "text": "And this is the river that Olympus was built on the side of."
  },
  {
   "start": 347.46,
   "end": 349.46,
   "text": "Right here."
  },
  {
   "start": 349.46,
   "end": 359.52,
   "text": "The river."
  },
  {
   "start": 359.52,
   "end": 363.62,
   "text": "Pretty close."
  },
  {
   "start": 363.62,
   "end": 370.07,
   "text": "Let's see how tall the people were."
  },
  {
   "start": 370.07,
   "end": 371.07,
   "text": "Can I walk in here?"
  },
  {
   "start": 371.07,
   "end": 375.07,
   "text": "Oh, it's a little bit higher than my head."
  },
  {
   "start": 375.07,
   "end": 379.07,
   "text": "Probably not tall enough for a 2 meter person to walk in, but."
  },
  {
   "start": 379.07,
   "end": 385.93,
   "text": "And then, let's see if the mosaic is anywhere over here."
  },
  {
   "start": 385.93,
   "end": 388.93,
   "text": "I saw the picture of the mosaic."
  },
  {
   "start": 388.93,
   "end": 394.46,
   "text": "Well, these here's where the baths were."
  },
  {
   "start": 394.46,
   "end": 399.78,
   "text": "Interesting."
  },
  {
   "start": 399.78,
   "end": 400.78,
   "text": "Pretty interesting."
  },
  {
   "start": 400.78,
   "end": 401.78,
