   "text": "It still has standing columns."
  },
  {
   "start": 410.41,
   "end": 411.41,
   "text": "What is this?"
  },
  {
   "start": 411.41,
   "end": 412.41,
   "text": "Very interesting."
  },
  {
   "start": 412.41,
   "end": 413.41,
   "text": "It's all about."
  },
  {
   "start": 413.41,
   "end": 414.41,
   "text": "The, it's the palaistra."
  },
  {
   "start": 414.41,
   "end": 420.23,
   "text": "It was where the athletes would get oiled up and practice."
  },
  {
   "start": 420.23,
   "end": 436.88,
   "text": "Um, and I think all the competitions were done there in the, uh, Hippodrome, the Coliseum."
  },
  {
   "start": 436.88,
   "end": 437.88,
   "text": "But, uh, that's what it looked like in the day."
  },
  {
   "start": 437.88,
   "end": 438.88,
   "text": "That one."
  },
  {
   "start": 438.88,
   "end": 439.88,
   "text": "And it's big."
  },
  {
   "start": 439.88,
   "end": 455.64,
   "text": "And I don't know if they re-erected these or what the deal is."
  },
  {
   "start": 455.64,
   "end": 456.64,
   "text": "Because, it's pretty crazy."
  },
  {
   "start": 456.64,
   "end": 460.64,
   "text": "It's amazing that they're still standing after all these years."
  },
  {
   "start": 460.64,
   "end": 461.64,
   "text": "Pretty cool."
  },
  {
